 like that it's more in the conversation.\\\"\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conversation\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Glover knows she has had to be the guinea pig,having first returned in Covid times for the TokyoOlympics, where she finished fourth.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2515, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Glover\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"the guinea pig\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2428}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid times\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"the TokyoOlympics\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She retired after that, spent more than a year out of the boat and performed the second retirement U-turn of her career.\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 2570, \"to\": 2578}, {\"ngram\": \"the second retirement\", \"from\": 2593, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"U\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2616}, {\"ngram\": \"turn\", \"from\": 2617, \"to\": 2621}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The return was gradual.\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2661, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The return\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2648}]}, {\"sentence\": \"First were the trials in November 2022.\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did those and won.\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2724, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She also won a trial a month later and has not looked back.\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2784, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a trial\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 Olympic Games rowing schedule in full: Events, UK start times and dates A stickler for s